      "side": 1,
      "message": "Personally I would inline this everywhere so readers of the code can avoid having to look up a function in another file. It\u0027s down to personal preference, but mine is for tests to be extremely easy to understand (esp. in isolation) even if it makes them verbose and inefficient.",
      "revId": "599d138fd5290c1d09b554da05cf1ac88a7c8b1a",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
